The Traveling Wilburys - Rare Studio Sessions 1988-1990

This is my edit of the Bootleg: 'The Traveling Wilburys - The Complete Collection' 
that I downloaded from Mega some years ago. I left out all the Demo versions of 
songs that had a official release on The Traveling Wilburys Vols I & III albums.
